{"tid":749296,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Comcast宣佈退出, Disney贏得21st Century Fox併購權","createTime":"2018-07-20T02:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T09:38:01.000Z","uid":64191,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ba6a8dbeb8428708291cf683aff901fba46c8bb1","tid":749296,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"美國有線電視與媒體巨擘康卡斯特（Comcast）今天表示，退出競購媒體大亨梅鐸的21世紀福斯公司（21st Century Fox）電影與電視業務的權利，由迪士尼公司贏得收購。<br />\n<br />\n康卡斯特發表聲明表示，將把重心轉向歐洲付費電視服務營運商天空集團（Sky）收購案。這顯示康卡斯特對最新一回合媒體娛樂產業合併案的立場改變。<br />\n<br />\n康卡斯特此舉等於確定迪士尼（Disney Co.）將能完成收購福斯的交易，創建產業的新火車頭，反觀梅鐸（Rupert Murdoch）卻縮減他的媒體帝國版圖。（譯者：陳宜君/核稿：羅苑韶）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/3262392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5641%2F3262392&d=KR2iNJyhpgUPMk8BaXJNfQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=b75ab62b\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/3262392</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/q7vct8alrzh01.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fq7vct8alrzh01.gif&h=05ec0b0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd0d5538674486f6bfaa5f565b84473484fddbd6","tid":749296,"uid":186784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba6a8dbeb8428708291cf683aff901fba46c8bb1","tid":749296,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"美國有線電視與媒體巨擘康卡斯特（Comcast）今天表示，退出競購媒體大亨梅鐸的21世紀福斯公司（21st Century Fox）電影與電視業務的權利，由迪士尼公司贏得收購。<br />\n<br />\n康卡斯特發表聲明表示，將把重心轉向歐洲付費電視服務營運商天空集團（Sky）收購案。這顯示康卡斯特對最新一回合媒體娛樂產業合併案的立場改變。<br />\n<br />\n康卡斯特此舉等於確定迪士尼（Disney Co.）將能完成收購福斯的交易，創建產業的新火車頭，反觀梅鐸（Rupert Murdoch）卻縮減他的媒體帝國版圖。（譯者：陳宜君/核稿：羅苑韶）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/3262392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5641%2F3262392&d=KR2iNJyhpgUPMk8BaXJNfQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=b75ab62b\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.